    "title": "Nike India is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Nike India! We are hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Navi Mumbai team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Nike India:\nNike India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nike India!",
